snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's VR: Help Wanted
snippet.description:
The first teaser trailer for upcoming VR title: "Five Nights at Freddy's VR: Help Wanted".
Available this Spring on Sony PSVR, HTC Vive and Oculus Rift!

Five Nights at Freddy's VR: Help Wanted is a collection of games from the Five Nights universe created by Scott Cawthon.
